d for diamond. Lastly, Rayleigh expressions for the rotational shot noise\nheating for a symmetric top-like particle for linear, elliptically, and\nunpolarized light are also provided.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 Sep 2019 22:11:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 7 Apr 2020 19:43:57 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 12 Aug 2020 17:14:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-16"}
