ng}$-mode. All the numerical models we report here also show a set of high\nfrequency oscillations at the vertical epicyclic and breathing mode\nfrequencies. The vertical oscillations show a 3:2 frequency ratio with\noscillations occurring approximately at the radial epicyclic frequency, which\ncould be of astrophysical importance in observed twin peak, high-frequency\nquasi-periodic oscillations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 14 Sep 2019 00:10:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-08"}
