ults. It suggests that exploring higher-order interactions\nprovides additional information not seen in graph representations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 14 Sep 2019 01:50:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 2 Jan 2020 17:53:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-03"}
